        {
            "title": "深水灣泳灘老婦遇溺 泳客救起送院搶救",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"警員到醫院調查。劉漢權攝\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/bf432553de960a7cde44ad6f05aed05f/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250418/_2025041808343222344.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">警員到醫院調查。劉漢權攝</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>黃竹坑香島道深水灣泳灘，今（18日）早上約8時，一名老婦在泳灘游泳期間遇溺，被其他泳客發現，將她救起。救護員接報到場，將老婦送律敦治醫院救治，警方正調查事件。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4201864/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"遇溺老婦被送往律敦治醫院治理。劉漢權攝 \" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/31e9e25c4e9d644e9048440a140eb231/2025-04/KakaoTalk_20250418_082516410.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        遇溺老婦被送往律敦治醫院治理。劉漢權攝 \n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
